snippet.title: RUNE II: Decapitation Edition Steam Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
RUNE II: Decapitation Edition launches November 13, 2020. Wishlist RUNE II on Steam at https://rune2.com/wishlist
 
Awaken, wolf of Midgard. I entreat your journey continue. It is a new age, and Hel, ruler of the Underworld and daughter of the foul trickster Loki has a message for you.

Purchase RUNE II on Steam from 11/13/2020 - 11/30/2020 and receive a free set of Dragon Armor!

** Follow RUNE II on Social Media! **
